<bibRefCitation id="EFD04B24FF80FF8BFD5D0BE8FCA239F3" author="Tigrero, J. O." box="[674,848,696,722]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" refId="ref60141" refString="Tigrero, J. O. (1998) Revision de especies de moscas de la fruta presentes en el Ecuador. Published by the author, Sangolqui, Ecuador. 55 p." type="book" year="1998">Tigrero (1998)</bibRefCitation>
and additional measurements kindly provided by Ing. Tigrero. The measurments of the terminalia are those he provided in the description; the length/width ratio of the aculeus tip in Tigrero's fig. 82 is less than that based on the measurements.
</paragraph>
